## Description {#details}

Wrapper for a function that represents a value that functionally represents the original function.

This can be a function, global alias to a function, or an ifunc.

Definition at line 941 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/constants-h">Constants.h</a>.
